This repository contains independent reimplementations of the rules of
tic-tac-toe, 2048, and Sokoban for benchmarking purposes. No source code
from the reference implementations is included or distributed.

Benchmark reference implementations (fetched separately by the user, not
part of this distribution):
- pgx (https://github.com/sotetsuk/pgx), Apache License 2.0
- Jumanji (https://github.com/instadeepai/jumanji), Apache License 2.0

Sokoban benchmark levels are generated by this repository
(djinnax/soko_levels.py); the Boxoban dataset is not used or distributed.
